{"tid":2118383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"意大利請屎為5G食lemon  駐意CEO自圓其說：商業考慮非政治因素","createTime":"2020-07-21T12:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T08:46:51.000Z","uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"42dafb16f6456b5816c3d5dee44afd0f631160f0","tid":2118383,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:12:20.000Z","msg":"繼英國在早前宣佈於未來的 5G 網絡建設計劃中停用華為的設備後，令其於歐洲市場的業務再受打擊。近日華為意大利總裁 Luigi De Vecchis 在接受意大利日報《晚郵報》訪問時就華為近日於當地 5G 網絡建設招標失敗一事發表意見，表示相關決定僅出於商業考慮，並非因政治因素。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華為意大利總裁 Luigi De Vecchis 日前在接受當地媒體採訪時就表示，<span class=\"gold\">華為在早前被當地電訊商意大利電訊 (Telecom Italia) 拒絕合作建設 5G 網絡一事全是出於商業上的考慮，並非如英國般出於政治因素而作出決定</span>。他又指出華為一方在得知相關消息後亦表示尊重意大利電訊的決定，並希望繼續現時非 5G 網絡外的合作關係。<br />\n <br />\nLuigi De Vecchis 在訪問中又透露意大利當局將在拒絕華為的參與後繼續與意大利電訊以及 Vodafone 等電訊商合作，試圖盡快決定計劃的供應商。據悉，在今個月初意大利為用於處理敏感數據的核心網絡基礎設施供應商進行招標時，當局並未有邀請華為參與。<br />\n<br />\nOn999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7b7c9b8418b65351f27f473b6a340a02e3a35c","tid":2118383,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"Source <a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/07/21/huawei-says-its-working-with-telecom-italia-despite-5g-exclusion/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F07%2F21%2Fhuawei-says-its-working-with-telecom-italia-despite-5g-exclusion%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=ddb7d834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/07/21/huawei-says-its-working-with-telecom-italia-despite-5g-exclusion/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"04d9a4dc072ac7511a2b8b0a6843646bdc4f64a3","tid":2118383,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"最後冇華為咪ok la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85450ad2036da2bfae6929ee466072022a2e10d","tid":2118383,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38d3333356ba1d3e084ad6f83f8b20d44bcac5f","tid":2118383,"uid":86224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"冇華為份就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}